{"tid":1549792,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中六丁丁想補習","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T20:02:14.000Z","uid":198133,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c0c9563c8074235a200b69201652c181440b51","tid":1549792,"uid":198133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"想問下補英文邊間同邊個好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家坐二望三<br />\n想上到四<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識揀邊間好啲"},{"pid":"cb0076ee9b43653a06eebff734e65b0b6fa5716e","tid":1549792,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d51a76b52e3967f35c3ad74bf428457b85dd758","tid":1549792,"uid":4526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:41:08.000Z","msg":"補牙龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e42d944b6301fb0e2f84ca8d750a1ab582b9b14","tid":1549792,"uid":145314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"Pm"},{"pid":"cec81c6a99e8860909c06fb922fc4